The objective of the present trial is: - to determine the dose limiting toxicity (DLT), maximal tolerated dose (MTD) and recommended phase 2 dose (RP2D) of intramuscular electrotransferred Plasmid AMEP in patients with advanced or metastatic melanoma.

 - to determine the local and general safety of intramuscular electrotransferred Plasmid AMEP - to evaluate the efficacy of intramuscular electrotransferred Plasmid AMEP